    <div class="wiki-section">
    <h3>Welcome to the Mercurialis Inc. Wiki</h3>
    <p>
        Mercurialis Inc. (MINC) stands as a shining beacon in the vast universe of EVE Online—a corporation rooted in history, camaraderie, and a relentless pursuit of excellence. Established during the beta phase of EVE Online in 2002, MINC is one of the longest-standing corporations in New Eden, embodying resilience, adaptability, and unity. Over two decades later, we remain a cornerstone of the EVE Online community, where legends are forged and new opportunities await.
    </p>
    <p>
        This wiki serves as the ultimate repository of knowledge for all things Mercurialis Inc. Whether you're a seasoned capsuleer, a wide-eyed recruit, or simply curious about our legacy, this wiki is your gateway to understanding the core of who we are and what we do. Through these pages, you'll gain insight into our operations, history, doctrines, and the tools that keep us ahead of the curve in the ever-evolving universe of EVE.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="wiki-section">
    <h3>Our History: A Legacy of Perseverance</h3>
    <p>
        From humble beginnings in the chaotic days of EVE's beta phase, Mercurialis Inc. has grown into an enduring powerhouse. Our journey has been punctuated by every major event in New Eden’s history, from the colossal battles of nullsec to the stealthy operations of wormhole space. We have weathered storms, built empires, and stood shoulder-to-shoulder with allies to defend the ideals we hold dear.
    </p>
    <h4>Highlights of Our Legacy:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>The Early Years (2002–2006):</strong> As pioneers in EVE Online’s beta phase, MINC quickly established a reputation for boldness and innovation. These formative years were marked by rapid growth, exploration, and the forging of alliances that would shape our future.</li>
        <li><strong>The Great Wars (2006–2012):</strong> During a period of intense conflict across New Eden, MINC was at the forefront of major alliances, contributing to some of the most legendary battles in EVE history. Our pilots became known for their expertise in fleet operations, intelligence gathering, and adaptability under fire.</li>
        <li><strong>The Age of Exploration (2012–2017):</strong> As the game evolved, so did we. MINC expanded its horizons into wormhole space, capital production, and the pursuit of cutting-edge technologies to ensure our dominance.</li>
        <li><strong>The Modern Era (2017–Present):</strong> Today, MINC is a diverse, multicultural corporation that thrives in both PvP and industry. Our continued success lies in the strength of our community and our commitment to staying ahead of the curve.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="wiki-section">
    <h3>Why Join Mercurialis Inc.?</h3>
    <p>
        At MINC, we believe that every capsuleer has a unique role to play in our shared journey. Whether you’re drawn to large-scale fleet battles, intricate industry projects, or covert operations, there’s a place for you here.
    </p>
    <h4>What We Offer:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Camaraderie:</strong> We’re more than just a corporation—we’re a family of like-minded pilots who support each other both in-game and beyond.</li>
        <li><strong>Opportunities for Growth:</strong> From new recruits to veteran pilots, everyone is given the tools and guidance to succeed in their chosen path.</li>
        <li><strong>Cutting-Edge Tools:</strong> As the official users of the Eve Rift Intel Fusion Tool (RIFT), we empower our pilots with the best intelligence-gathering capabilities available.</li>
        <li><strong>Diverse Playstyles:</strong> Whether you prefer mining in the safety of our industrial fleets or diving into the chaos of nullsec PvP, MINC provides a platform for every playstyle.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

