<div class="wiki-section">
    <h3>Stay Connected</h3>
    <p>
        The heart of Mercurialis Inc. lies not only in our achievements but in our connections with one another. To foster this sense of community, we provide multiple avenues for communication and collaboration:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>In-Game:</strong> Join our official channel, <em>MINC BAR</em>, to connect with fellow pilots and leadership.</li>
        <li><strong>Discord:</strong> Our Discord server is the central hub for planning operations, sharing insights, and socializing with other members.</li>
        <li><strong>Eve Rift Intel Fusion Tool (RIFT):</strong> Take advantage of our powerful intelligence tool, designed specifically for the EVE community to stay ahead of adversaries.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

